  <POU Name="Cell_Services_Prog" Id="{425107ba-9f67-4a23-b822-bdc63beb5685}" SpecialFunc="None">
    <Declaration><![CDATA[(*!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
Program Used to handle all Ancillary Service Requests for All Robots
Service Requests include Mastering Test, Brake Test, Tip Change and Tip Dress
	author: Brent Lekx-Toniolo of Sodecia GTAC
	July, 2013
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
REVISION NOTES:
	Date: October 2014
	- Added capability of up to 30 robots, b.lekx-toniolo
	Date: December 2014
 	- changed All_Robots_Clear MAIN.Rx.Task_ID_Ack from 250 to 350, b.lekx-toniolo
 	- added NOT  GTAC_CONFIG.Under_Construction TO Robot_Reqs_masterTest and BrakeTest and TipChange, JVD
	Date: March 2015
	- added/changed code to force Master and Brake Test Ext and allow all robots to ack such before starting full master or brake tests, blt
	Date: May 2016
	- added config data to auto configure code, b.lekx-toniolo (blt)
	Date: June 2017
	- broke out IF formatiing in task_id code, b.lekx-toniolo (blt)
	Date:May 2021 
	-Cleaned up Steppers Reset  to ensure that ALL steppers that are enabled are checked (CD)
	-Cleaned up Tip Change Requests to be easier to read and troubleshoot (CD)
	Date: June 2024
	- Massaged in TraccTCP code developed / tested by Wes Griffiths on project 2302901 (blt)
	Date: Sept 2024
	- Correction to Start brake Test code as per SSCC610 GH Issues #140, (blt and wg)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*)

